msgstr "具有相同的篩選條件。"

msgid "Has the same sort criteria."
msgstr "具有相同的排序條件。"

msgid "Has the same pager settings."
msgstr "具有相同的分頁器設定。"

msgid "Has the same contextual filters."
msgstr "具有相同的情境篩選器。"

msgid "There are no path-based displays available."
msgstr "目前沒有可用的以路徑為基礎的顯示方式。"

