"<code>$settings['package_manager_composer_path'] = "
"'@composer_path';</code>. See <a href=\":url\">this change record</a> "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"Composer "
"的路徑是在設定中指定的，但此作法已不再支援。要修正此問題，請執行 "
"<code>composer require 'composer/composer:@version'</code>，將 "
"<code>composer/composer</code> "
"加入專案的相依套件，<em>或</em> 在 "
"<code>settings.php</code> "
"中加入以下一行：<code>$settings['package_manager_composer_path'] "
