msgstr "提供用於描述產品的額外 Open Graph Protocol meta 標籤。"

msgid "Undefined group '%group' on tag '%tag'"
msgstr "在標籤「%tag」中有未定義的群組「%group」"

msgid ""
"A set of meta tags specially for controlling the summaries displayed "
