msgstr ""
"取消勾選下方你不希望任何 Webform "
"使用的可選外部程式庫。"

msgid ""
"The default sender address for emailed webform results; often the "
"email address of the maintainer of your forms."
msgstr ""
"用於透過電子郵件寄送 Webform "
"結果的預設寄件者地址；通常是表單維護者的電子郵件地址。"

msgid "Select available submission handlers"
msgstr "選取可用的提交處理器"

msgid "Wizard previous"
msgstr "導引流程：上一步"

msgid "wizard previous"
msgstr "導引流程：上一步"

msgid "Wizard next"
msgstr "導引流程：下一步"

msgid "wizard next"
msgstr "導引流程：下一步"

msgid "Computed settings"
msgstr "計算後設定"

