"The <strong>Upload</strong> page allows a CSV (comma separated values) "
"file or URL to be uploaded, converted, and imported into webform "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"<strong>上傳</strong>頁面可讓您上傳 "
"CSV（逗號分隔值）檔案或 URL，並將其轉換後匯入至 "
