"An example of a condition could be when viewing a certain node type "
"and blocks should be placed as a reaction when viewing a page with "
"this node type."
msgstr "條件的一個例子是：當檢視特定的內容節點類型時，系統會在檢視具有此節點類型的頁面時，作為回應放置區塊。"

